payload.sql: SELECT users.*, 3958.755864232 * 2 * ASIN(SQRT(POWER(SIN((35.6894875 - users.latitude) * PI() / 180 / 2), 2) + COS(35.6894875 * PI() / 180) * COS(users.latitude * PI() / 180) * POWER(SIN((139.6917064 - users.longitude) * PI() / 180 / 2), 2))) AS distance, CAST(DEGREES(ATAN2( RADIANS(users.longitude - 139.6917064), RADIANS(users.latitude - 35.6894875))) + 360 AS decimal) % 360 AS bearing FROM "users"  WHERE (users.latitude BETWEEN 35.25529215066746 AND 36.12368284933254 AND users.longitude BETWEEN 139.157108535901 AND 140.22630426409899 AND 3958.755864232 * 2 * ASIN(SQRT(POWER(SIN((35.6894875 - users.latitude) * PI() / 180 / 2), 2) + COS(35.6894875 * PI() / 180) * COS(users.latitude * PI() / 180) * POWER(SIN((139.6917064 - users.longitude) * PI() / 180 / 2), 2))) <= 30) ORDER BY distance
